## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on publicly available online sources, which may not provide a comprehensive view of the topic. Additionally, the debate around euthanasia is deeply personal and influenced by cultural, religious, and individual beliefs, which can vary widely. The report does not cover all possible perspectives and may not fully capture the nuances of the ethical and moral arguments involved. Further research, including empirical studies and expert interviews, would be beneficial for a more in-depth understanding.